text: Man of the Woods is the fifth solo studio album by American entertainer Justin Timberlake. It is set to be released on February 2, 2018, two days before his halftime performance at Super Bowl LII. The first single from the album, "Filthy", was released on January 5, 2018. == Track listing == == References == Category:Justin Timberlake albums Category:2018 albums
